headline: Kraft Heinz's Stock Is as Cheap as It's Been Since 2020. 1 Thing to Know Before You Buy.
summary: Two years later, they merged the entity with Kraft Foods to create Kraft Heinz.  According to many valuation metrics, Kraft Heinz stock is a bargain right now.  Kraft Heinz is a combination of two iconic businesses.
